[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Wagon speed limits]]


Sets whether speed limits should apply for wagons that set them. The default wagons in the game do not specify a maximum speed, so this feature only affects wagons from [[en/Manual/NewGRF]] sets.

== Use ==

This feature is enabled by default. You can disable this patch through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Advanced Settings/Vehicles#enable-wagon-speed-limits|configure patches --> vehicle]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:

 [patches]
 wagon_speed_limits = false
